course.assignments.completed, 0), totalAssignments: courses.reduce((sum, course) => sum + course.assignments.total, 0), totalStudyTime: courses.reduce((sum, course) => sum + course.studyTime, 0), upcomingDeadlines: courses.reduce((sum, course) => sum + course.upcomingDeadlines.length, 0), overallProgress: courses.reduce((sum, course) => sum + course.progress, 0) / courses.length }; // Learning analytics data const learningAnalytics = { peakStudyHours: [14, 15, 16, 19, 20], // 2-4 PM and 7-8 PM weakSubjects: courses.filter(course => course.grade.includes('B') || course.grade.includes('C')), strongSubjects: courses.filter(course => course.grade.includes('A')), studyStreakDays: 12, averageSessionLength: 2.5 // hours }; const getGradeColor = (grade) => { if (grade.startsWith('A')) return 'text-green-600'; if (grade.startsWith('B')) return 'text-blue-600'; if (grade.startsWith('C')) return 'text-yellow-600'; return 'text-red-600'; }; const getPriorityColor = (priority) => { switch(priority) { case 'high': return 'text-red-600 bg-red-50 border-red-200'; case 'medium': return 'text-yellow-600 bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-200'; case 'low': return 'text-green-600 bg-green-50 border-green-200'; default: return 'text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 border-gray-200'; } }; return (
